raw_videos.description:
From Ricky's Family:
Please watch this video! Just for a little background, this is my cousin Ricky. He had leukemia and ended up passing away January 5th. He loves your pizza reviews and decided to make his own while hospitalized. I'd love for you to watch it. If there is any way you could post this video in memory of him for his anniversary, January 5th that would be amazing! He has a brother and a lot of friends who I know it would make really happy! Even his mom loves you so I know it would make her happy as well. Your videos brought a lot of joy to him while he was in the hospital so thank you for everything
